gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Warriors 134, Lakers 120
gameRecap.excerpt: The Warriors defeated the Lakers 134-120. Klay Thompson recorded 27 points, five 3PM, and three assists for the Warriors, with Stephen Curry adding 23 points (6-6 3PM), eight assists, and seven rebounds in the victory. LeBron James tallied 33 points, 11 assists, and seven rebounds for the Lakers in the losing effort. The Warriors improve to 44-35, while the Lakers fall to 45-35.
